{
  "page": "Benfrey Frey",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\"><img alt=\"House Frey.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/50px-House_Frey.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/75px-House_Frey.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/100px-House_Frey.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Benfrey Frey</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Benfrey_Frey\" title=\"Benfrey Frey\"><img alt=\"Benfrey Frey.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f2/Benfrey_Frey.svg/50px-Benfrey_Frey.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f2/Benfrey_Frey.svg/75px-Benfrey_Frey.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f2/Benfrey_Frey.svg/100px-Benfrey_Frey.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Benfrey_Frey_by_Lopata_4.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Benfrey Frey by Lopata 4.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/c2/Benfrey_Frey_by_Lopata_4.jpg/350px-Benfrey_Frey_by_Lopata_4.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"424\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/c2/Benfrey_Frey_by_Lopata_4.jpg/525px-Benfrey_Frey_by_Lopata_4.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/c2/Benfrey_Frey_by_Lopata_4.jpg/700px-Benfrey_Frey_by_Lopata_4.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Benfrey by Lopata Four</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\">House Frey</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Rivermen\" title=\"Rivermen\">Rivermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_270_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">270</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_279_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">279&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/299_AC\" title=\"299 AC\">299&#160;AC</a><br />the <a href=\"/index.php/Twins\" title=\"Twins\">Twins</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey\" title=\"Walder Frey\">Walder Frey</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Mother</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Bethany_Rosby\" title=\"Bethany Rosby\">Bethany Rosby</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouse</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Jyanna_Frey\" title=\"Jyanna Frey\">Jyanna Frey</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Della_Frey\" title=\"Della Frey\">Della Frey</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Osmund_Frey\" title=\"Osmund Frey\">Osmund Frey</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">Personal arms</span></th><td>\nThe arms of Frey and Rosby, quartered<sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;N 1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup><br /><i>(Quarterly clockwise, 1st and 3rd Cendrée, a bridge azure, at either end a tower of the same; 2nd and 4th Ermine three chevronels gules)</i></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (appears)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (appendix)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Benfrey Frey</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\">House Frey</a>. He is the sixteenth son of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey\" title=\"Walder Frey\">Walder Frey</a>, the second by his sixth wife, Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Bethany_Rosby\" title=\"Bethany Rosby\">Bethany Rosby</a>. Benfrey married his cousin <a href=\"/index.php/Jyanna_Frey\" title=\"Jyanna Frey\">Jyanna Frey</a> with whom he has two children, <a href=\"/index.php/Della_Frey\" title=\"Della Frey\">Della</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Osmund_Frey\" title=\"Osmund Frey\">Osmund Frey</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Family\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Family</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Notes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance\">Appearance</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Benfrey_Frey&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Benfrey resembles his sister <a href=\"/index.php/Roslin_Frey\" title=\"Roslin Frey\">Roslin</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> He is a younger <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Benfrey_Frey&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Benfrey_Frey&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>When Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Edmure_Tully\" title=\"Edmure Tully\">Edmure Tully</a> arrives at the <a href=\"/index.php/Twins\" title=\"Twins\">Twins</a> for his wedding, Benfrey is ordered by Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey\" title=\"Walder Frey\">Walder Frey</a> to lead his sister <a href=\"/index.php/Roslin_Frey\" title=\"Roslin Frey\">Roslin</a> into the hall. After Roslin and Edmure meet for the first time, Walder has Benfrey return his sister to her chambers.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>During the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Wedding\" title=\"Red Wedding\">Red Wedding</a>, Benfrey grabs <a href=\"/index.php/Dacey_Mormont\" title=\"Dacey Mormont\">Dacey Mormont</a> by the arm, but she smashes a flagon full of <a href=\"/index.php/Wine\" title=\"Wine\">wine</a> in his face and wrenches free.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Benfrey_Frey&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Benfrey dies of a wound he receives at the wedding.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Benfrey_Frey&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Benfrey, see your <a href=\"/index.php/Roslin_Frey\" title=\"Roslin Frey\">sister</a> back to her chambers, she has a <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Wedding\" title=\"Red Wedding\">wedding</a> to prepare for.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey\" title=\"Walder Frey\">Walder Frey</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Brenett</b>: Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Bethany_Rosby\" title=\"Bethany Rosby\">Bethany</a> gave Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey\" title=\"Walder Frey\">Walder</a> a child every year.<br />\n</p><p><b>Catelyn</b>: How many lived past infancy?<br />\n</p>\n<b>Brenett</b>: Five. Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Perwyn_Frey\" title=\"Perwyn Frey\">Perwyn</a>. Ser Benfrey. Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Willamen_Frey\" title=\"Willamen Frey\">Willamen</a>, who took his vows last year and now serves <a href=\"/index.php/Eon_Hunter\" title=\"Eon Hunter\">Lord Hunter</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Vale_of_Arryn\" title=\"Vale of Arryn\">the Vale</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Olyvar_Frey\" title=\"Olyvar Frey\">Olyvar</a>, who squired for your <a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">son</a>. And Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Roslin_Frey\" title=\"Roslin Frey\">Roslin</a>, the youngest.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Brenett\" title=\"Brenett\">Brenett</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Benfrey_Frey&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey\" title=\"Walder Frey\">Walder</a></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Bethany_Rosby\" title=\"Bethany Rosby\">Bethany<br />Rosby</a></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td></tr><tr align=\"center\"><td style=\"border-right:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:1em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td><div style=\"width:1em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td></tr>\n<tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td><div style=\"width:1em; height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:1em; height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black;\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div><